<section>
	<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
	<p>
		truckload.io for iOS is committed to protecting your privacy. We do not collect, store, or transmit any
		personal information. All data — including your loads, cargo items, and configurations — is stored locally
		on your device and never leaves the app.
	</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>Data Storage</h2>
	<p>
		All information is saved in secure on-device storage on your iPhone or iPad. We do not synchronize or back
		up your data to any external servers unless you choose to do so via iCloud or other device-managed backups.
	</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
	<p>
		truckload.io does not integrate any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services. The app
		functions entirely on-device, ensuring no external data collection or network dependency.
	</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>Policy Updates</h2>
	<p>
		We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect improvements or changes in the app. Any significant revisions
		will be posted here with the date of the version release.
	</p>
</section>

<section>
